{"tid":527239,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)復仇勇者 八惡人 逆天奇緣  秒速殺機","createTime":"2018-01-12T12:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T20:58:51.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e15c49a6758f3af133e065f2bcabdacc65d3c9","tid":527239,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=pTR%2FEUkjdOgxdBYR81dsTKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=9f7891ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=pTR%2FEUkjdOgxdBYR81dsTKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=0947dc66\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\nimg]<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/2a/The_Revenant_2015_Poster.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F2a%2FThe_Revenant_2015_Poster.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=pTR%2FEUkjdOgxdBYR81dsTKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=fe5eaf30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/2a/The_Revenant_2015_Poster.jpg[/img]</a><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/08/The_Hateful_Eight_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F08%2FThe_Hateful_Eight_Poster.jpg&h=7193da7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/71/Upside_Down_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F71%2FUpside_Down_poster.jpg&h=e19b457e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/90/Mechanic_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F90%2FMechanic_poster.jpg&h=a0cb3255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1823年，由毛皮貿易商安德魯&middot;亨利隊長率領的一群狩獵者，來到美國密蘇里領地、現為北美大平原的一片冰雪叢林中狩獵毛皮。狩獵途中，他們遭到當地美洲原住民阿里卡拉族的伏擊，而阿里卡拉族人剛好在尋找被白人擄走的酋長的女兒，因此將他們視為威脅。狩獵隊伍大部分人被屠殺，餘眾逃到船上後撤離。領隊及最富經驗的毛皮獵人休&middot;格拉斯，因為熟識當地的地形及瞭解原住民的追蹤方式，亨利於是拋棄了船..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事設定於美國南北戰爭後的六年、八年或十二年左右，一輛驛馬車在正值冬天的懷俄明州的雪地中疾駛而過。車上的乘客是正要帶著通緝重犯杜黛詩前去紅石小鎮領賞金的賞金獵人尊洛夫。途中，他們遇見兩個陌生人：曾為北軍騎兵的惡名昭彰的賞金獵人華馬龍、自稱為紅石鎮新警長的孟基斯。在暴風雪中，四人躲進一間驛馬車站避難。迎接他們的不是驛站主人米妮，而是另外四張陌生面孔..<br />\n<br />\n3.宇宙中充滿著神奇，在某個地方存在這樣一種系統：兩個靠得很近的星球圍繞同一個太陽轉動，這兩個星球的引力僅對來自於自身的物質產生影響，卻影響不到另一星球的物質。一個星球上物體的重量能被來自另一星球上的等量物質抵消，但來自於不同星球的物質相互接觸，一段時間之後就會燃燒殆盡。本劇劇情就在這樣的環境裡展開&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n4.故事敘述一名職業殺手亞瑟&middot;畢夏（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）不但武藝高強、槍法神準，也心思縝密，手法乾淨俐落，在殺完人後會將死者看起來像意外、自殺或被另有人他殺的模樣，以避免警方的追捕。<br />\n劇情一開始，亞瑟聽信老闆迪恩（東尼&middot;高德溫飾）的謊話，誤以為恩師哈利（唐納&middot;蘇德蘭飾）背叛組織，奉命謀殺哈利，亞瑟誘導哈利到了他布置好的現場時，哈利放棄了抵抗，還幫助亞瑟做好自己被劫車的搶匪開槍打死的假象，所以亞瑟心懷愧疚..<br />\n<br />\n8 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=pTR%2FEUkjdOgxdBYR81dsTKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=7aa9dcf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=pTR%2FEUkjdOgxdBYR81dsTKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=cc90a64e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f17d016cdee8be2fffd29407a18b4aa00600c62","tid":527239,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/2a/The_Revenant_2015_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F2a%2FThe_Revenant_2015_Poster.jpg&h=52a5f599&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbb03d0ad3223ecd1adb9465c98dfcb67f4f0c9c","tid":527239,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f480e980bb7355afc97fd413aa42318d366633","tid":527239,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2775209bdabfe4efa0245a4c64b80ffefa5295","tid":527239,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1742918bf5f372cc32eb5ff284899ba34ec40fb","tid":527239,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c8b36ba83b776b2c0fb61b1efda83f93393cf3","tid":527239,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif